      • pruneInvalidMessages

        protected static java.util.Collection<org.projectfloodlight.openflow.protocol.OFMessage> pruneInvalidMessages(java.lang.Iterable<org.projectfloodlight.openflow.protocol.OFMessage> msgList,
                                                                                                              java.util.Collection<org.projectfloodlight.openflow.protocol.OFMessage> valid,
                                                                                                              org.projectfloodlight.openflow.protocol.OFVersion swVersion,
                                                                                                              boolean isActive)
        Sorts any invalid messages by moving them from the msgList. The net result is a new list returned containing the invalid messages and a pruned msgList containing only those messages that are valid for the given role of the controller and OpenFlow version of the switch.
        参数:
        msgList - the list of messages to sort
        valid - the list of valid messages (caller must allocate)
        swVersion - the OFVersion of the switch
        isSlave - true if controller is slave; false otherwise
        返回:
        list of messages that are not valid, removed from input parameter msgList
